title: Alexander's Tomb T1 T3 (2008 - 2012) (Sosich) cbr
description:
Alexandria, June 1858.Grave robbers are engaged in a fierce battle to capture the  treasures of the ancient catacombs. Among them, seven French nationals discover the ruins of an underground chapel devoted to Alexander the Great...the conqueror's tomb can not be far away... Brought together by the promise of wealth,seven adventurers seek the only manuscript that can guide them to the tomb through an underground maze filled with water.But they are not the only ones looking.Intrigues,conspiracies,betrayals and murders will play out in this unusual treasure hunt...

enjoy
